    <item>
      <title>诺福克南方公司将支付 6 亿美元以和解漏油案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/norfolk-southern-to-pay-600-million-to-settle-ohio-spill-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺福克南方公司 (Norfolk Southern Corp.) 表示，将支付 6 亿美元来解决去年俄亥俄州火车脱轨事件引发的诉讼，该事故导致超过 100 万加仑有毒化学品泄漏并导致居民患病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/norfolk-southern-to-pay-600-million-to-settle-ohio-spill-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blue Owl 通过 Prima 收购进军房地产金融</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/blue-owl-pushes-into-real-estate-finance-with-prima-acquisition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blue Owl Capital Inc. 正在推出一项房地产融资战略，收购了 Prima Capital Advisors，并从 GIC Pte 聘请了 Jesse Hom 来带头实施这一战略。一份声明证实了彭博新闻社早些时候的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/blue-owl-pushes-into-real-estate-finance-with-prima-acquisition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
